Productivity & Advanced Commands
/model [sonnet|opus]: Switches the active LLM model during the session.
/effort [low|medium|high|max]: Adjusts the thinking depth and token budget for complex tasks.
/plan: Switches to "Plan Mode" to analyze the codebase and generate a strategy without making immediate edits.
/mcp: Manages Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers to extend Claude's capabilities with external tools.
/doctor: Diagnoses and verifies your installation, environment, and settings for troubleshooting. 

