Common Keyboard Shortcuts
Shift+Tab: Cycles between permission modes: Default (asks for everything), Accept Edits, and Plan Mode.
Esc (Twice): Quickly opens the /rewind menu.
Ctrl+C: Cancels the current model generation or input.
Ctrl+G: Opens an external editor for easier multi-line input.